sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin/User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCInitialization Controller
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster Controller
    participant ManifestMgr as Manifest Manager
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ServiceMesh as Service Mesh<br/>Istio
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Admin,Prometheus: Flow 1: Component Deployment

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>kubeconfig auth
    K8sAPI-->>DSCICtrl: Watch notification
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>ServiceMesh: Configure ServiceMeshControlPlane<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy monitoring stack<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR<br/>kubeconfig auth
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification
    DSCCtrl->>ManifestMgr: Request component manifests
    Note over ManifestMgr: Manifests embedded at build time<br/>from GitHub repos
    ManifestMgr-->>DSCCtrl: Return kustomize manifests
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply component manifests<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Component resources created
    Note over K8sAPI: Component pods start

    Note over Admin,Prometheus: Flow 2: Monitoring and Metrics

    Prometheus->>DSCCtrl: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    DSCCtrl-->>Prometheus: Operator metrics
    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: Scrape component ServiceMonitors<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: Component metrics

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Access Prometheus Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS OAuth
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: OAuth Proxy validates token
    K8sAPI->>Prometheus: Forward request<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS (internal TLS)
    Prometheus-->>K8sAPI: Metrics data
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: Response

    Note over Admin,Prometheus: Flow 3: Secret and Certificate Generation

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create Secret with annotation<br/>kubeconfig auth
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: SecretGenerator watches
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Generate random secret values<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: Secret populated

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Certificate CR (cert-manager)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over K8sAPI: cert-manager issues certificate
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: CertConfigmapGenerator watches
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap from cert data<br/>ServiceAccount Token
